  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Patterned after the fiery blades masterfully wielded by some&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/outsiders/angel\">angels</a>, the split-blade sword is both a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment---final/goods-and-services/toys-games-puzzles#TOC-Holy-Symbol\">holy symbol</a>&nbsp;and a difficult-yet-effective weapon. A split-blade sword resembles a large&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment---final/weapons/weapon-descriptions/scimitar\">scimitar</a>&nbsp;whose blade splits into two about two-thirds of the way toward the tip. If your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;score is less than 15, you take a –2 penalty on attacks rolls with a split-blade sword, as you’re unable to maneuver its unusual blade.</p>",
